OL,3,CWorld's oldest topiary garden
OL,4,Cundergoes extensive six-month trim
OL,6,FThe dedicated team of four gardeners
OL,7,Fmeticulously prune a variety of
OL,8,Fdesigns, ranging from chess pieces and
OL,9,Fpeacocks to characters like Homer
OL,10,FSimpson, Darth Vader, and Queen
OL,11,FElizabeth I.
OL,13,FOne of the most challenging tasks is
OL,14,Fthe maintenance of the "Great
OL,15,FUmbrella," a towering sculpture
OL,16,Fstanding at 10 metres.
OL,18,FThis intricate work requires the use
OL,19,Fof a cherry picker, with gardeners
OL,20,Fleaning out at considerable heights to
OL,21,Fensure precision.
